This product includes methodologies and procedures inspired by, but not copied from,
the open-source projects listed in ATTRIBUTION.md. No leaked system-prompt full text
is included; only publicly observed patterns are summarized under an "inspired-by"
policy. See ATTRIBUTION.md for source-by-source license status and integration mode.

FableLayer does not transplant model capability. It applies only the procedures whose
transferability was empirically observed (verification grounding, completion/evidence
gating, systematic investigation, early-stop prevention, structured output). Performance
claims are backed exclusively by the reproducible benchmark in bench/ with stated limits.
